    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This FYI RFC is a bibliography of information about TCP/IP internetworking, prepared by the User Services Working Group (USWG) of the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF).  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify any standard. [Also FYI 3.]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
